subject: FBR Open (Golf)
lead_paragraph: J. B. Holmes shot a six-under-par 65 to share the clubhouse lead with Doug LaBelle II at nine-under 133 among the players who finished the second round Friday at the FBR Open in Scottsdale, Ariz. LaBelle shot a 64. A 90-minute frost delay to start the day left 45 golfers on the course when play was halted because of darkness.One of them, Camilo Villegas, was tied for the lead at nine under through 12 holes. Two were at eight under on the course: Bill Haas through 13 holes and Ben Crane through 14. They will complete the round Saturday before the cut is made.
